                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. has been affected by humudity and shows traces of extensive use: many fols. are stained with dirt, wax or humidity. The text on several fols. is partly illegible, e.g., <locus target="1r">1r</locus> (discoloured), 1v, 2r, 8r, 8v, 9r. The back board has been broken and repaired. The sewing has been damaged and crudely repaired. Both boards seems to have been reused (there are sets of holes on the outer edges). <locus target="33">33</locus> is of smaller size (damaged by rodents?).</condition>
